  <official_title>A RANDOMIZED, DOUBLE-BLIND, PLACEBO-CONTROLLED STUDY TO ASSESS THE SAFETY AND EFFICACY OF A NOVEL ORAL ACNE TREATMENT FOR THE TREATMENT OF ACNE VULGARIS</official_title>
